接口 HistogramDataPoint

  • 所有超级接口:
    Cloneable
    所有已知子接口:
    iHistogramRowSeq.Iterator
    所有已知实现类:
    HistogramAggregationIterator, HistogramDownsampler, SimpleHistogramDataPointAdapter

    public interface HistogramDataPoint
extends Cloneable
    Represents a single histogram data point, e.g. all of the buckets for a measurement at a point in time.
    从以下版本开始:
    2.4

        long timestamp()
        Returns the timestamp (in milliseconds) associated with this data point.

      • getRawData

        byte[] getRawData(boolean include_id)
        Get the encoded value of this histogram. NOTE: implementation should store the serialize information in the byte array so latter it can decide how to deserialize it back
        返回:
        The encoded value os this histogram data point
